description: This file is a C header file that declares exported API functions for the CCSP CWMP Soap Parser Object. It includes function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling, and initializing the soap parser object, serving as an interface for other components to interact with the CCSP CWMP SOAP parser.

methods.name: CcspCwmpCreateSoapParser
methods.description: Creates a SOAP parser object with provided container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: CcspCwmpSoappoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the SOAP parser object with specified contexts.

methods.name: CcspCwmpSoappoRemove
methods.description: Removes the SOAP parser object instance.

methods.name: CcspCwmpSoappoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls the necessary objects for the SOAP parser.
